        "faq0": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What furniture do you sell?",
            "content": "<p>Proferlo stocks bed frames and bases, bedroom furniture (including bedside tables and tallboys), living room furniture (sofas, coffee tables, TV units, and shelving), and dining furniture (dining tables and chairs). We're an online-only Australian furniture store — no showroom, just great pieces shipped directly to your door.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "faq1": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Do you have a showroom?",
            "content": "<p>No — Proferlo is an online-only store. Our warehouse is located in Acacia Ridge, Brisbane, but it's a dispatch facility only and is not open to the public. All orders are placed through our website and delivered Australia-wide.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": true
          }
        },
        "faq2": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Where do you ship?",
            "content": "<p>We ship Australia-wide via Allied Express. Metro areas typically receive orders in 2–4 business days. Regional and remote delivery timeframes may vary — contact us for a delivery estimate to your area.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "faq3": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What's your return policy?",
            "content": "<p>We offer 14-day risk-free returns. If you're not happy with your purchase, contact our team within 14 days of delivery and we'll arrange a return. Items must be in original condition and packaging.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "faq4": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Are your products easy to assemble?",
            "content": "<p>Most Proferlo pieces require basic self-assembly and come with clear instructions and all required hardware. Assembly typically takes 30–60 minutes for most items. If you have any issues, our support team is happy to help.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "faq5": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How do I contact you?",
            "content": "<p>You can reach us via the contact form on our website or by emailing us directly. We're an online-only business, so our team operates digitally — we aim to respond to all enquiries within 1 business day.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        }
